Modular build: Change HashTree() to use the tree snapshot abstraction

This will make it possible to ignore .git/.svn directories when
hashing output trees, in a later change.

We change ListFiles() to use tree snapshots, and extend snapshots to
support symlinks.

Move HashFile() to dirtree.py because that is where it is now used.

